name: Warung Nasi Babi Guling (Soly)
address: HF3W+C9F, Jl. Baledan, Duda Tim., Kec. Selat, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80862, Indonesia
review 1: Its a surprise I get this place in my review lost ! Its in the middle of no where and i found it while I was riding from blue lagoon becah to bisalhi temple , and I stopped because I was very hungry and she gave me a mix of everything , rice , veggies , dried fish, sambal, chicken , tofu, and soybean , it tasted delicious and 1.5 ltrs of water all to get her I paid 21000idr ! Amazing place , they have babi gulling as well but I didn't try , but maybe some esle would try ! I recommend if your wantering on the most beautiful back roads of Bali and you find this shop ! Stop for a snack or food , they Evan had a lot of small home made snacks !
review 2: Tried babi guling for the first time, very good food, low price and polite staff. Restaurant is s table in the market. Recommend this to everyone, very good flavors
review 3: Delicious and friendly host. Come here with a big heart & an even bigger stomach to fill your belly with a little taste of Balinese heaven. But please Don't tell everyone!

pork meat is delicious, soup is good and spicy.
review 5: We paid 60k per person only for main menu and cold meal.. Be careful.. it could be a tourist trap if you are not a local...
